  "body": "<div id=\"post-view220221775275\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea220221775275\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">이수한의원 환자분께서 오늘도 몸에 좋은걸 주셨어요. </p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">바로..</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/830a0587bc2da901.jpg\" width=\"548\" height=\"414\" style=\"cursor: pointer;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rheight: 414px; rwidth: 548px;\" id=\"20141227_62/isuhani_1419646136008OcYiJ_JPEG/PC263850.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000033463D9DAB')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/830a0587bc2da901.jpg\"></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />9번 덖고 아홉번 말린 '구기자차' &amp; 내몸을 맑게해주는 '우엉차'에요</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">이걸루 차끓여 먹을생각하니 벌써부터 몸이 건강해지는 느낌이들어요 ㅋㅋ<br />너무 오바가 심한가? 헤헤<br />그래두 그런걸 어떡해요 ^^</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">그냥 말린것도 아니고 9번씩이나 덖고 9번씩이나 말렸다는 과정이 너무 정성이&nbsp;가득하자나요. </p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/2fbf59ce9c48c9ee.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"416\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 416px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20141227_237/isuhani_1419646240602yr7IW_JPEG/PC263842.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000033463D9DAB')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/2fbf59ce9c48c9ee.jpg\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/4021693c0b2f5010.jpg\" width=\"550\" height=\"416\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 416px; rwidth: 550px;\" id=\"20141227_5/isuhani_1419646240832AGqkR_JPEG/PC263843.JPG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000033463D9DAB')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/4021693c0b2f5010.jpg\"></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">환자분께서도&nbsp;그만큼 저희에게 정성을 주시는건데 </p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">우엉차 &amp; 구기자차 마시구 조금이라도 더 건강해져서<br />이번 겨울 따뜻하게 잘보냈으면 좋겠습니다 ^^ </p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br /></p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">감사합니다 ^^<br />&nbsp;</p></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
